content: I'll definitely check out Kanemasa for kanimeshi and Tsukiji Itadori Uogashi Nihon-Ichi for namashirasu. I've also been wanting to try some grilled squid, so maybe I'll stop by the Yokohama Central Market to see what they have. By the way, do you know if there are any autumn festivals or events happening in Yokohama during the next few weeks?
